<subSubSection id="6DE165012511FF90FF4510B8FD6BFDDA" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="2544368A2511FF90FF4510B8FD6BFDDA" blockId="4.[178,1085,490,629]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">
Comment: The original description is based on a male 
<typeStatus id="FA4088282511FF90FCDA10B8FC14FDAF" box="[813,902,490,512]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<specimenCount id="33FDFD032511FF90FC4C10B8FBAFFDAF" box="[955,1085,490,512]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" type="generic" typeStatus="paratypes">17 paratypes</specimenCount>
from &quot;Mt. Ohtakisan, 
<collectingRegion id="E73FF8682511FF90FE60135AFDB4FDB1" box="[407,550,520,542]" country="Japan" name="Kagawa" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">Kagawa Pref.</collectingRegion>
&quot; (
<bibRefCitation id="416A4B7B2511FF90FDCA135AFD66FDB1" author="WATANABE Y" box="[573,756,520,542]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" pagination="29 - 37" refId="ref11582" refString="WATANABE Y. (1991): New species of the group of Lathrobium pollens (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae) from Shikoku, Japan. - Journal of the Speleological Society of Japan 16: 29 - 37." type="journal article" year="1991">WATANABE 1991</bibRefCitation>
). Some of the above specimens are teneral. The similar modifications of the male sternites VII and VIII, as well as the similarly derived morphology of the aedeagus suggest that 
<taxonomicName id="E2FB4D092511FF90FCCC1311FC59FDF7" authorityName="WATANABE" authorityYear="1991" box="[827,971,578,600]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanukiense">
<emphasis id="178FEA982511FF90FCCC1311FC59FDF7" box="[827,971,578,600]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">L. sanukiense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="E2FB4D092511FF90FEE01332FDABFDDA" authority="WATANABE 1992" authorityName="WATANABE" authorityYear="1992" box="[279,569,607,629]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="shingon">
<emphasis id="178FEA982511FF90FEE01332FE10FDDA" box="[279,386,607,629]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619">L. shingon</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="416A4B7B2511FF90FE7E1332FDABFDDA" author="WATANABE Y" box="[393,569,607,629]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1619" pagination="189 - 196" refId="ref11621" refString="WATANABE Y. (1992): New species of the group of Lathrobium pollens (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae) from Western Honshu, Japan. - Elytra, Tokyo 20 (2): 189 - 196." type="journal article" year="1992">WATANABE 1992</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and allied species.
</paragraph>
